otherNames: 快穿之顶级反派要洗白
synopsis: I was a big boss. After I was reborn, I became a poor person. In order to change my fate, I traveled through space and time, trying to change the fate of tragedy, but in the process of changing my fate, I was always kissed by him in the bathtub, on the bed and in the wilderness! After a few times, I fell into deep thought. Was the answer to the mystery? Changing fate meant kissing?
